### AuthLogin
post http://{{host}}/api/auth/login HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "foo",
  "password": "foo123"
}

### AuthRefresh
post http://{{host}}/api/auth/refresh HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{token}}"
}

### Videos
get http://{{host}}/api/video HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### UserInfo
get http://{{host}}/api/user/info HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### RefreshVideos
post http://{{host}}/api/video/refresh HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
